data.description: Say Hello to your new lake home! 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and 900 square feet make this the perfect weekend getaway! Inside the kitchen is open to the living room and offers plenty of counter and cabinet space. Both bedrooms are spacious with large closets. Outside you have a new metal carport offering covered parking and a large deck just off the living room. And best of all, a short gently sloping walk down to the water.
